mil.nga.giat.geowave.core.store.metadata

Class DataStatisticsStoreImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.core.store.metadata.AbstractGeoWavePersistence<DataStatistics<?>>
      • mil.nga.giat.geowave.core.store.metadata.DataStatisticsStoreImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataStatisticsStore

    public class DataStatisticsStoreImpl
extends AbstractGeoWavePersistence<DataStatistics<?>>
implements DataStatisticsStore
    This class will persist Index objects within an Accumulo table for GeoWave metadata. The adapters will be persisted in an "INDEX" column family. There is an LRU cache associated with it so staying in sync with external updates is not practical - it assumes the objects are not updated often or at all. The objects are stored in their own table.
